De_Parthe - Bomb Defusal
Mapped by Kev (Xj2)
Based upon De_Parthenon by Cloune

This is a remake of the map de_parthenon by Cloune. Rebuilt from scratch to look nicer with improved fps. The map is fairly open and uncluttered for fast paced play on large servers.

The original map can be found here - [url]http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/8039[/url]
